{"tid":1427324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨派和理非必須團結一致：五大訴求、缺一不可","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T06:08:59.000Z","uid":63095,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"da54652829b768a2ce2a5db8ae0726eaba746c5b","tid":1427324,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:47:11.000Z","msg":"身為一名獨派，我明有好多勇武手足唔只要爭取五大訴求，心底仲希望一次過爭取獨立，但始終香港獨立仍未成為社會大風氣，即使係民主派入面都有好多人未接受到，而且香港政府已經刻意將呢場運動勾上港獨，試圖分化獨派同和理非，並藉此打壓。<br />\n<br />\n我同意今次運動可以暗地宣揚港獨，游說和理非認清香港獨立係唯一出路，但呢埸運動訴求必須團結一致，集中爭取五大訴求，否則只會重蹈14年雨革被分化嘅覆轍！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n<br />\n2. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n<br />\n3. 必不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求、缺一不可</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港、時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2ea39c8cf93bb68db922fc84434e7b76f2a90d95","tid":1427324,"uid":63095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:48:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求、缺一不可</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f98fa9ea10d81c2b5bba911fc5bc319fdc5bc3f2","tid":1427324,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"98d9fa7d72217abcecdc2e571cd701c127efeabb","tid":1427324,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d3d07ead6a7d4721a2eeb2f8ec14d04aa682991a","tid":1427324,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"31704083572a2352d2c5e121810e4ef692f1bf22","tid":1427324,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:53:45.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"75be1345e6ceb0c3a50ddfc84ae8563da6d8